summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 5811 for the improvement of West Myrtle Street, from 30th Avenue Southwest to 35th Avenue Southwest; and certain parts of certain other streets and avenues; by grading and otherwise improving the same; under Ordinance No. 76629 as amended by Ordinance No. 76845, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
